    p This time of year never fails to evoke a feeling of childhood nostalgia in us all. Whatever age you are, I don't think those memories of anticipation and mixed emotions for the start of a new school year ever leave us. A crisp new uniform hanging in the wardrobe with shiny new school shoes, a brand new pencil case filled with stationary waiting to be opened! However brilliant your summer holibobs had been there was always a definite sense of readiness and excitement to get back to school and back into your normal routine, and to catch up with your friends and make new ones… or perhaps I was just a massive geek! 
    
